        <p>- Good faith and transparency - the data we collect, process and comply with the current privacy policy that is available to each user;</p>
        <p>- Relevance of treatment to objectives and minimization of data - Data types, which we collect, are minimized according to the purposes for which they are being processed. We process only the data, for which we have the legal rights for its processing or we process the data, for which we have obtained your consent; - storage limitation - process and store received data for a period of time, according to the purposes for which they are needed and your consent.</p>
